Bloomberg’s Muse arts and culture
team welcomes top figures in a range of fields from music to
museums, academia to design, theater, and architecture.  Among this summer’s roster of notable visitors were: crime
novelist Linda Fairstein; musician David Bromberg; food and
humor writer Calvin Trillin; and Bard College President  Leon Botstein .  To contact the editor responsible for this slideshow:
Lili Rosboch at +1-212-617-2191 or
 Erosboch2@bloomberg.net .
 